                     <td valign="top" class="TableCell">Yay! The first batch of miniatures have arrived back from the manufacturer and in James' words, they are perfect! I took delivery
                        of 30 Thundra Beasts and RIders last Friday and I must admit they are pretty good. 
                        <p></p>If you would like any of the miniatures in particular  (good pictures are <a href="http://www.faszination-fantasy.de/zinnfigindex.htm" class="linka">here</a>) then let us know by posting in the Merchandise forum. T'Skrang and Windlings will probably be first off the line...
