                  <tr>
                     <td valign="top" class="TableCellAlternate">Most FASA Earthdawn RPG books and novels are now available to your friendly  local gaming store. Effective immediately, any
                        store wishing to stock FASA Earthdawn books can now do so through Centurion Hobby Distributors. Please pass the word, and
                        let you local gaming store know. If your local store does not currently have an account with Centurion, their contact information
                        is as follows:
                        <p></p><b>Centurion Hobby Distributors</b><br>www.centurion-hobby.com<br>Centhobby@aol.com<br><br>1-888-657-1802 TOLL FREE<br>1-732-537-1004<br>1-732-537-1187<br><p></p>Centurion will only sell to stores, and NOT the general public. PLEASE do not attempt to contact them for direct purchases.
                        Instead, give their contact information to your local store.
                        <p></p>
                     </td>
                  </tr>
